help on categories help on categories categories are used to group pages to make a category first create a new page for it by convention it should be named category x where x might be home page question or whatever word or short phrase describes the category when creating the category page start it off with the category template to add a given page to that category simply place a link to the category page within that page normally these go at the bottom such as the category forum help link on this page that's all if you then check back at the category page you ll see the other page listed you can create as many categories as you want and pages can be in any number of different categories just create a link to each category page category forum help close window site home california classical association help on categories
